node.text: goodbye Chicago!!! I really really enjoyed our time here - I’ve been here a few times but really never fully took advantage of your city until this trip. Officially now one of my favorite places to visit. And for the record, your food feedback sent us to @loumalnatis, @portilloshotdogs and @stansdonutschicago! love u guys. Will be back soon. Next stop, back to LA, getting kids ready for their first day of preschool and kindergarten!! Ahhhh! Xx

node.text: CHICAGO! my belly needs your help!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by chrissy teigen on September 05, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, food and indoor.

node.text: working on my cookbooks with @adeenasussman is always my most favorite job. no one cooks better, no one has a more creative brain, and no one gives life advice like this woman. I don’t know what I would have done without this woman in my home one year ago. I really fucking love what we have created together, my work wife. You can pre-order Cravings: All Together now! It shot to number 7 in all of Amazon books and number one in comfort food cooking, toot toot!!
